From Ann Carlson Subject Re Homosexuality issues in Christianity In article M , Bryan Whitsell writes Any one who thinks that Homosexuality and Christianity are compatible should check out Romans I Corinthians I Timothy Jude II Peter Gen Lev to name a few of the verses that pertain to homosexuality Anyone who thinks being gay and Christianity are not compatible should check out Dignity, Integrity, More Light Presbyterian churches, Affirmation, MCC churches, etc Meet some gay Christians, find out who they are, pray with them, discuss scripture with them, and only then form your opinion Dr Ann B Carlson O MS o NASA Langley Research Center Hampton, VA